title: Flore Laurentienne - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Flore Laurentienne performing live at the Conservatoire de Rennes 
Auditorium in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2023. Recorded December 8, 2023. 

Songs:
Fleuve I
Petit Piano
Autriche III
Voiles

Mélanie Bélair - Violin
Chantal Bergeron - Violin
Ligia Paquin - Viola
Sylvain Murray - Cello
Antoine Létourneau-Berger - Percussion, Marimba, Synth, Guitar
Robbie Kuster - Percussion, Synth
Mathieu David Gagnon - Organ, Electric piano, Minimoog, 12 string guitar

Audio Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Guest Audio Engineer: Pierre Girard
Audio Mixer: Pierre Girard
Mastering: Pierre Girard
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
